如果两个值不能直接比较大小，那么就把他们的差值与0作比较。
            ——数学老师
所以，实现思路如下
(使用高端的[url=http://www.mcbbs.net/thread-533943-1-1.html]pcb[url]格式)
//建立计分板{
init:/scoreboard objectives add score dummy
init:/scoreboard players set A score a
init:/scoreboard players set B score b
init:/scoreboard players set off score 0 
//一会要用的（储存差）
init:/scoreboard objectives setdisplay sidebar score
//}
//运算部分{
icb:/scoreboard players operation off score = A score
//将a值储存，以免计算时改变
/scoreboard players operation off score -= B score
//（用储存的值）执行a-b
/scoreboard players test off score 1
cond:/say a>b
/scoreboard players test off score -1000000 -1
cond:/say a<b
/scoreboard players test off score 0 0
cond:/say a=b
/scoreboard players set off score 0
//清空储存的a
//}
复制代码
